OOC: Why did Talos never recieve Sunhawk's
transmission.

--- Jonathan <jhogan@...> wrote:
> > "yo boss, do ya have a plan or do we just shoot
> them all?"
> > Quickstrike asked Megatron while a venom blast at
> Kup.
> >
> 
> {Talos}
> 
>     Talos watched the battle raging around the
> energon sphere, the strange
> female bot whose very presence seemed to radiate
> authority and power hung
> over the sphere not inclined to join the chaos of
> the battle but didn't seem
> overly distraught by everyone attempting to kill
> each other.
> 
>     When the alarm sounded on his interior monitor
> he growled in
> frustration, "Grimlock, Kup and Kenzo, disengage!
> Trouble back at base check
> it out we'll continue the fight."
> 
> Snarling Talos charged forward towards megatron the
> blast sheild up before
> him attempting to tackle the predicon leader and
> take the fight to a more
> melee stance. "Close and engage everyone take it to
> them, I don't want a
> stray shot clipping that raw energon!"
> 
> {Grimlock}
> 
>     Growling Grimlock ignored Talos' order stomping
> forward, chasing the
> retreating Waspinator his twin abrreled hand cannon
> discharging another dual
> volley of energy blasts..."Me Grimlock no retreat,
> me Grimlock stomp
> predicons!"
> 
> 
>
